    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Golf-wear, Reimagined",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Let's be honest: golf style hasn't always kept pace with how women actually live. It's either overly sporty or overly traditional. Rarely both elevated and wearable. Varley changes that.</p><p>With a collection that seamlessly blends performance fabric with lifestyle silhouettes, Varley creates pieces that move with you through morning tee times, afternoon errands, coffee runs, travel days, and everything in between.</p><p>It's functional, but not fussy. Relaxed, but refined. The kind of clothing you throw on without thinking twice and somehow always look pulled together.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
        "text_1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
    },
