    "text_3": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "For the Woman Who Moves And Moves Well",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>What sets Varley apart is its understanding of real life.</p><p>The detail is in the drape. The fabric is featherlight but structured. Quarter-zips are cut just right at the collarbone, vests layer cleanly over fitted tops, and joggers hug without clinging. These aren't pieces made just for the course, they're made for the in-between moments, too: warming up, winding down, or heading out for a spontaneous 9.</p><p>You're just as likely to spot Varley in a club locker room as you are at brunch, at school pickup, or on a red-eye. That's the brilliance of it, it belongs everywhere without ever feeling out of place.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
        "text_1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
    },
