    "text_4": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "On-Course Calm, Off-Course Ease",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>When it comes to performance, Varley keeps things subtle but smart. Moisture-wicking, breathable, stretch-friendly, all the essentials are there. But what elevates the brand is how effortlessly those features are built into pieces that feel pulled from your favorite lifestyle wardrobe.</p><p>It's not \"golfwear you can wear anywhere.\" It's just great clothing that happens to be perfect for golf.</p><p>And in a category where many brands still feel like they're trying to catch up to women's real style sensibilities, Varley leads by simply knowing what works.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
        "text_1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
