    "text_5": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Why It Works",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At its core, Varley is about ease. Not just in movement, but in mindset. It strips away the stiffness from traditional golf style and replaces it with quiet confidence. You're not dressing to play a role, you're dressing to feel like yourself.</p><p>That's the kind of fashion that lasts. And in the golf world, where personality and presence are finally being welcomed into the fold, Varley is showing up right on time.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
